text:
What networks do subscribers leave from: actual MNP data

02 Nov 2019, 14:01

The Ministry of Finance portal, citing data from the Ukrainian Center for Radio Frequencies, published information about which subscribers most often use the number transfer service (MNP). In general, the service has not become very popular; throughout the country, the number of numbers transferred is tens of thousands.
On October 29, 2019, the largest number of numbers transferred from the operator was recorded at Vodafone Ukraine - 11,865.
Data on operators by the number of numbers transferred to the network:

Kyivstar - 10,860;
Vodafone Ukraine - 8565;
Intertelecom - 154;
lifecell - 8972;
"Trimob" - 629.

Data on operators by the number of numbers transferred from the network:

Kyivstar - 11,477;
Vodafone Ukraine - 11,865;
Intertelecom - 47;
lifecell - 5385;
"Trimob" - 406.

